@startuml
[*] --> Order : «M» New Plane Acquired/

state Order
Order --> Arrival : «M» Plane Arrived/
state Arrival
Arrival --> Preparation : «M» Arrival Processing/

state Preparation
Preparation --> Operations : «M» Condition OK & Schedule Available/
Preparation --> Maintenance : «M» Needs Maintenance/

state Operations
Operations --> Maintenance : «M» No More Flights/Maintenance Required/

state Maintenance
Maintenance --> Preparation : «M» Checked & Serviced/

Operations --> Retired : «M» No Longer Available/
Maintenance --> Retired : «M» No Longer Available/

state Retired <<final>>
@enduml
